OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will be a mixture of
OL,6,Fbright spells and occasional sunny
OL,7,Fintervals along with some showers,
OL,8,Fthese possibly on the heavy side in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FAnother mixed day with some
OL,14,Fbrighter spells but also some showers,
OL,15,Fperhaps heavy in the Borders. Lighter
OL,16,Fwinds but a bit colder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
