OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FSaturday starting dry before cloud and
OL,7,Frain push up from the south. Dry much
OL,8,Fof Sunday then rain spreading from
OL,9,Fnorthwest later, lasting into Monday
OL,10,Fbefore brightening up later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
